    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header class="hero">
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Nanotechnology</h1>
            <p>Exploring the science and engineering of materials at the nanoscale to create revolutionary technologies</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="section" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">What is Nanotechnology?</h2>
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <p>Nanotechnology is the science, engineering, and application of materials and devices at the nanoscale—typically between 1 and 100 nanometers. At this scale, materials exhibit unique physical, chemical, and biological properties that differ significantly from their bulk counterparts, opening up possibilities for revolutionary technologies across multiple industries.</p>
                    <p>As a nanotechnology engineer, you'll work at the intersection of physics, chemistry, biology, materials science, and engineering to design, fabricate, and apply nanomaterials and nanodevices. You'll develop techniques to manipulate matter at the atomic and molecular level, creating materials with enhanced properties such as increased strength, lighter weight, greater chemical reactivity, or novel electronic characteristics.</p>
                    <p>This rapidly evolving field is driving innovations in medicine, electronics, energy, materials, and environmental remediation. From targeted drug delivery systems to quantum computing components, nanotechnology is transforming our technological capabilities and addressing some of society's most pressing challenges.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Areas Section -->
    <section class="section bg-dark" id="key-areas">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Key Areas of Study</h2>
            <p class="section-intro">Nanotechnology encompasses critical disciplines for developing and applying nanoscale materials and devices:</p>
            
            <div class="cards-grid three-columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-atom"></i> Nanomaterials</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Synthesis, characterization, and application of materials at the nanoscale.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Carbon Nanostructures</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Nanotubes, graphene, fullerenes</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Nanoparticles</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Metallic, semiconductor, polymeric</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Quantum Dots</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Optical, electronic properties</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-microchip"></i> Nanoelectronics</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Development of electronic components and devices at the nanoscale.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Quantum Computing</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Qubits, quantum gates</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Molecular Electronics</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Single-molecule devices</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Spintronics</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Electron spin-based devices</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-microscope"></i> Nanofabrication</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Techniques for creating structures and devices at the nanoscale.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Lithography</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">E-beam, photolithography</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Self-Assembly</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Bottom-up fabrication</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Nanoimprint</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Pattern transfer techniques</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cards-grid three-columns" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-dna"></i> Nanobiotechnology</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Application of nanotechnology to biological systems and medicine.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Drug Delivery</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Targeted therapies, nanocarriers</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Biosensors</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Disease detection, monitoring</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Tissue Engineering</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Nanoscaffolds, regenerative medicine</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-solar-panel"></i> Nanoenergy</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Nanotechnology applications in energy generation, storage, and efficiency.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Solar Cells</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Quantum dot, perovskite</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Energy Storage</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Batteries, supercapacitors</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Fuel Cells</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Nanocatalysts, membranes</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i> Nanocharacterization</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Techniques for imaging and analyzing nanoscale materials and structures.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Electron Microscopy</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">TEM, SEM, STEM</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Scanning Probe Microscopy</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">AFM, STM techniques</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Spectroscopy</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">XPS, Raman, FTIR</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

